sentence: (RTTNews) - The Home Depot, Inc. (HD) revealed a profit for its fourth quarter that rose from last year.
The company's profit came in at $2.48 billion, or $2.28 per share.
This compares with $2.34 billion, or $2.09 per share, in last year's fourth quarter.
The company's revenue for the quarter fell 2.7% to $25.78 billion from $26.49 billion last year.

The Home Depot, Inc. earnings at a glance:

-Earnings (Q4): $2.48 Bln.
